Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一次突然的到访
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家 千鸟要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的组织要动真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定摧毁秘银 抢夺倾听者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抢夺的…难道是我?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汞合金已经在考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜使用武力也要得到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算把这个城市也变成一片火海吗
