Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是一名老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁 这里无关人员不得…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘同学你不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会劝说这些人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛闭上 常盘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵 没想到你是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前做什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测到瞄准波 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士 相良中士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来急救 你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士 还愣着做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天进出的教学楼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃午饭的中庭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近随处可见的公寓楼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医药店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽车公交
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可替代的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明战争已近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没有一个人察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己已经身陷战场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6点钟方向 距离0
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功率和机动性均高于地狱骑士型
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极度危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 相良
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的警告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有放弃抵抗 把她乖乖交出来的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的回答你应该很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会以为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不识时务是一种很帅气的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺讨厌你这种人的!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你能阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算让我爱你都行!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的勇敢和坚强…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会为了这种男人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动力装置 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电容器全部损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…弃…机逃离…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 AL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:23:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批准你…退役…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.23,0:23:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会走的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟谁走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.77,0:23:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.26,0:23:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.81,0:23:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了吧 相良
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会带你回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…一定会!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会带你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我只觉得那是一句苍白无力的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
